---
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="Privacy Policy"
	description="What information Tokyo Mix Style collects, how it's used, and the choices you have."
	pubDate={new Date('Jul 2 2026')}
	updatedDate={new Date('Jul 12 2026')}
>
	<p>
		This page explains what information Tokyo Mix Style collects when you visit this site, and
		what choices you have about it.
	</p>

	<h2>Analytics</h2>
	<p>
		We use Google Analytics (GA4) to understand which pages are popular and how visitors find the
		site. Google Analytics uses cookies to collect aggregated, anonymized information such as
		pages visited, general location (country or city level), device type, and how you arrived at
		the site. This information is not used to personally identify you. You can read more in
		<a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google's Privacy Policy</a>.
	</p>

	<h2>Affiliate links and cookies</h2>
	<p>
		This site participates in affiliate marketing programs, such as the Amazon Services LLC
		Associates Program and other retail affiliate networks. When you click an affiliate link,
		these programs may place a cookie on your device so that, if you make a purchase, the referral
		can be tracked back to this site and we can earn a small commission. This does not affect the
		price you pay. The specific programs we participate in may change over time; this page will be
		updated to reflect that.
	</p>

	<h2>Your choices</h2>
	<p>
		You can control or delete cookies at any time through your browser settings. To opt out of
		interest-based advertising more broadly, you can visit the Digital Advertising Alliance's
		opt-out page at
		<a href="https://www.aboutads.info/choices" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">aboutads.info/choices</a>.
		If you are a California resident, you may have additional rights regarding your personal
		information under the CCPA; you can reach out using the details on our
		<a href="/contact">Contact page</a> to ask about these rights.
	</p>

	<h2>Changes to this policy</h2>
	<p>
		We may update this page from time to time as the site or its affiliate partnerships change.
		The date above reflects the most recent update.
	</p>

	<h2>Contact</h2>
	<p>
		If you have questions about this policy, please get in touch via our
		<a href="/contact">Contact page</a>.
	</p>
</Layout>
